Package com.example.namesplitter.storage

Klasse InMemorySalutationService

java.lang.Object
com.example.namesplitter.storage.InMemorySalutationService
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
SalutationStorageService
public class InMemorySalutationService extends Object implements SalutationStorageService
The InMemorySalutationService class implements the SalutationStorageService interface and provides an in-memory storage for salutations. It uses a HashMap to store the salutations and provides a method to get all salutations. It follows the Singleton design pattern to ensure that only one instance of this class is created.
